<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFB76A08FD9F9C141CC0B15C" box="[611,704,2637,2670]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="76" pageNumber="834">Congo</collectingCountry>
River at elevations of 400-460 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
